North Korean leader Kim Jong-il dead

wiki.text:
'Iron Fist' may refer to:
* Iron Fist (comics), a Marvel Comics superhero/martial artist
* ''Iron Fist'' (novel), a 1998 Star Wars novel by Aaron Allston in the X-
  wing series
* ''Tekken'' (series) (鉄拳, lit. Iron Fist), a series of fighting games by Namco
* 20th Armoured Brigade (The Iron Fist), nickname of British Army armoured
  formation based in Paderborn, Germany
* Iron Fist (countermeasure), an Israeli counter-weapon system
* Iron Fists, a chapter of Space Marines in the Warhammer 40,000 universe
* Ironfist (Transformers), a character in the Transformers series
* [[The Man with the Iron Fists]], a film starring Russell Crowe

In 'music':
* ''Iron Fist'' (album), a 1982 album by metal band Motörhead ** "Iron Fist"
  (song), a single from the album
* Iron Fist, a progenitor of the band Helloween
* "Iron Fist", a song from Die Apokalyptischen Reiter's debut album Soft
  & Stronger
* "Iron Fist", a song from Goldfinger's album [[Disconnection Notice]]
* "Iron Fist", a song from Coheed and Cambria's 2013 album, [[The Afterman:
  Descension]]. In 'sports':
*  Dr. Ironfist, the Ukrainian heavyweight boxer and Ph.D., Vitali Klitschko
   (a.k.a. Dr. Eisenfaust)
